      <title>阿波罗购买桑坦德银行基础设施贷款组合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/apollo-buys-into-portfolio-of-santander-s-infrastructure-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻看到的一份声明显示，阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 已与西班牙桑坦德银行 (Banco Santander SA) 达成协议，投资 3.7 亿美元的基础设施贷款组合，此举旨在提高资本回报率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/apollo-buys-into-portfolio-of-santander-s-infrastructure-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 09:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
